name: TimesTables
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: times tables
des: Alexa will ask you 5 random multiplication questions from the 0 to 12 times tables. After each answer, Alexa will tell you if you answered correctly. After the final question, Alexa will tell you your score out of 5. If you tell Alexa to stop you won't get a score out of 5.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
